<html lang='uz'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Hisobni tasdiqlash — Food Express</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      .wrapper {
        padding: 32px 16px;
      }
      .card {
        max-width: 480px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .header {
        background: #328315;
        padding: 15px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .logo-wrap {
        width: 64px;
        height: 64px;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 50%;
        margin: 0 auto 16px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .header h1 {
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 30px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin: 0 0 4px;
      }
      .header p {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        font-size: 13px;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .body {
        padding: 24px;
      }
      .desc {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0 0 24px;
      }
      .otp-box {
        background: #f0faf0;
        border: 1.5px dashed #328315;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }
      .otp-label {
        font-size: 11px;
        color: #328315;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        margin: 0 0 8px;
      }
      .otp-code {
        font-size: 45px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #328315;
        letter-spacing: 12px;
        font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .otp-timer {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888;
        margin: 8px 0 0;
      }
      .warning-box {
        background: #fffbeb;
        border-left: 3px solid #f59e0b;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 12px 14px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }
      .warning-box p {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #92400e;
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .footer {
        background: #f9f9f9;
        border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        padding: 20px 24px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .footer p {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #999;
        margin: 0 0 4px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .footer .links a {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #aaa;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin: 0 6px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='wrapper'>
      <div class='card'>

        <div class='header'>
          <h1>Food Express</h1>
          <p>Tez va mazali yetkazib berish</p>
        </div>

        <div class='body'>
          <p class='desc'>
            Emailni tasdiqlash uchun kod. Bu kod
            <strong>3 daqiqa</strong>
            amal qiladi.
          </p>

          <div class='otp-box'>
            <p class='otp-label'>✦ Tasdiqlash kodi</p>
            <p class='otp-code'>{{code}}</p>
            <p class='otp-timer'>⏱ 3 daqiqa ichida muddati tugaydi</p>
          </div>

          <div class='warning-box'>
            <p>
              ⚠️ Ushbu kodni
              <strong>hech kimga bermang</strong>
              — Food Express xodimlari ham so'ramaydi. Agar siz bu so'rovni
              yubormagan bo'lsangiz, xabarni e'tiborsiz qoldiring.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>